<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OTP Email</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .otp {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #007bff;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .note {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #777;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #888;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h2>One Time Password (OTP) Verification</h2>
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>Your One Time Password (OTP) for verification is: <span class="otp">{{otp}}</span></p>
        <p>This OTP is valid for {{otpValidityMinutes}} minutes. Please use it to verify your account.</p>
        <p class="note">If you didn't request this OTP, please ignore this email.</p>
        <p class="footer">Thank you!</p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
